      <Text layoutX="49.0" layoutY="106.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="•Checkmate: this endgame occurs when one of the players is threatening the opponent’s king and it both cannot move to any other square and the checking piece cannot be captured or hindered." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="253.20843505859375">
