      <Text layoutX="45.0" layoutY="198.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="•Resignation: it occurs when one of the players believes that they will be checkmated soon and, for these reasons, they resigns instead of playing out the game." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="261.20843505859375">
