            <Font name="Courier New Bold" size="12.0" />
         </font>
      </Text>
      <Text layoutX="45.0" layoutY="283.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="•Timeout: it doesn’t matter how much of an advantage you have on the board, if you run out of time, you automatically lose the game!" textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="261.20843505859375">
