         </font>
      </Text>
      <Text layoutX="324.0" layoutY="106.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="•Stalemate: it occurs when one of the players isn't in check, but also cannot make any legal move." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="217.20843505859386">
